  "text": "It wouldn't be possible for any of us to have some type of contact with confederation or direct work. I am laying observing the distortions of those who underwent this experiential sequence. We decided to gradually back off, shall I say, from direct contact in thought form. The least distortion seems to be available in mind to mind communication, therefore the request to be taken aboard is not one we care to comply with. You are most valuable in your present orientation.",
